---
import blankProfilePicture from '../assets/blank-profile-picture.png'
import shaikhMusab from '../assets/SheikhMusab.png'
import shaikhSaid from '../assets/ShaikhSaid.jpg'
import shaikhYousif from '../assets/ShaikYousif1.jpeg'
import ustadAhmed from '../assets/UstadAhmed1.jpeg'
import sheikhAhmedSaeed from '../assets/sheikhAhmedSaeed.png'
---

<div class="bg-cyan-600 px-4 p-2 md:px-8 md:py-2 mx-auto mt-5">
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="rounded-xl text-gray-100 p-5">
            <h4 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl mb-10">Our Imams</h4>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap md:justify-between">
                <div class="w-full m-5 md:w-[48%] md:m-[1%] lg:w-[31%]">
                    <img src={shaikhSaid.src} alt="profile picture" class="rounded-full m-1 w-48 h-48 object-cover mx-auto" />
                    <h4 class="text-xl text-center my-5">SHAIKH SAID AHMED</h4>
                    <p class="my-3">Over 10 years of experience teaching Islamic studies and delivering Da'wah lectures.</p>
                    <p class="my-3">Proficient in Quran recitation and teaching Quran Tafseer with proper Tajweed</p>
                    <p class="my-3">Taught various students from diverse backgrounds, promoted Islamic manners and ethics</p>
                    <p class="my-3">Involved in curriculam development of various levels for the Quran program</p>
                </div>

                <div class="w-full m-5 md:w-[48%] md:m-[1%] lg:w-[31%]">
                    <img src={sheikhAhmedSaeed.src} alt="profile picture" class="rounded-full m-1 w-48 h-48 object-cover object-top mx-auto" />
                    <h4 class="text-xl text-center my-5">SHAIKH AHMED SAEED</h4>
                    <p class="my-3">Over 10 years of experience as an Imam, a teacher of Quran and Islamic Studies, proficient in Quran recitation and Hadeeth sciences.</p>
                    <p class="my-3">Imam at Al-Aelat mosque, Egypt delivering Jummah Khutbas</p>
                    <p class="my-3">Teaching Quran and Islamic studies at Fawaris Ahl Sunnaha, Egypt</p>
                    <p class="my-3">Imam at OIAC since 2021</p>
                </div>

                <div class="w-full m-5 md:w-[48%] md:m-[1%] lg:w-[31%]">
                    <img src={shaikhMusab.src} alt="profile picture" class="rounded-full m-1 w-48 h-48 object-cover mx-auto" />
                    <h4 class="text-xl text-center my-5">SHAIKH MUSAB</h4>
                    <p class="my-3">Taught Quran, Arabic and related subjects engagingly by infusing respect and passion for the Deen in the hearts of students.</p>
                    <p class="my-3"> Possesses a chain of narrations based on the narrations of Hafs on the authority of Asim tracing back to the Prophet Muhammad (PBUH), exemplifying his deep understanding of the Quran and Sunnah.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>